---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
// Tax Season Bookkeeping Readiness page
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Tax Season Bookkeeping Readiness — Projexions"
  description="A structured, one-time review for businesses approaching tax season with uncertainty. Get clarity before you talk to a CPA."
  currentPath="/tax-season-bookkeeping-readiness"
>
  <div class="page-container">
    <h1 class="serif-heading text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Tax Season Bookkeeping Readiness</h1>
    <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-12 text-center page-subtitle"><strong>Clarity before you talk to a CPA</strong></p>

    <div class="services-card">
      <div class="prose-content">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          When tax season hits, many businesses realize their books aren't as clean as they thought.
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          This service answers one question: <strong>What needs to be fixed before a CPA can file—and what can wait?</strong>
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">What You Get</h2>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>60-minute bookkeeping evaluation call</li>
          <li>Written Tax Readiness Map (PDF) delivered within 48 hours</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 text-center">
          No cleanup. No filing. No pressure.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Who This Is For</h2>

        <ul class="resource-list text-lg mb-6">
          <li>Solo founders, creators, e-commerce operators, small agencies</li>
          <li>Businesses unsure whether their records are usable for tax filing</li>
          <li>Anyone trying to avoid wasted time or money before engaging a CPA</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12 text-center">
          This is not for businesses seeking ongoing bookkeeping or tax advice.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Pricing</h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6 font-semibold text-center">
          <strong>$149</strong> · One-time
        </p>

        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-12">
          If you move forward with cleanup, the evaluation fee is credited toward the engagement.
        </p>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="section-title text-center">Schedule Your Evaluation</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          If your books are fine, you'll know. If they aren't, you'll finally know why—and what matters most.
        </p>

        <form name="evaluation-booking" method="POST" data-netlify="true" class="booking-form">
          <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="evaluation-booking" />

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-row">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="day">Preferred Day</label>
              <select id="day" name="day" required>
                <option value="">Select a day</option>
                <option value="Monday">Monday</option>
                <option value="Tuesday">Tuesday</option>
                <option value="Wednesday">Wednesday</option>
                <option value="Thursday">Thursday</option>
                <option value="Friday">Friday</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="time">Preferred Time</label>
              <select id="time" name="time" required>
                <option value="">Select a time</option>
                <option value="9:00 AM">9:00 AM</option>
                <option value="10:00 AM">10:00 AM</option>
                <option value="11:00 AM">11:00 AM</option>
                <option value="1:00 PM">1:00 PM</option>
                <option value="2:00 PM">2:00 PM</option>
                <option value="3:00 PM">3:00 PM</option>
                <option value="4:00 PM">4:00 PM</option>
              </select>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
            <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">Request Appointment</button>
          </div>
        </form>

        <hr class="section-divider">

        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Disclaimer</h2>
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Projexions provides organizational review and decision-support only. No accounting, tax, legal, or financial advice is provided.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .services-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    padding: 2.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    max-width: 750px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .section-divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    margin: 2.5rem 0;
  }

  .section-cta {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .booking-form {
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }

  .form-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .form-group {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .form-group label {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--text-gray);
  }

  .form-group input,
  .form-group select {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--ui-gray);
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    background: white;
  }

  .form-group select {
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  .form-group input:focus,
  .form-group select:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--brand-green);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .form-row {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
